                    Elite Pest Management
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    Professional pest control services for commercial,
                    industrial, residential, and institutional clients.
                </p>
                <div class="flex space-x-4">
                    <!-- Social Icons Placeholder -->
                    <a
                        href="#"
                        class="text-gray-400 hover:text-[var(--color-secondary)] transition-colors"
                    >
                        <span class="sr-only">Facebook</span>
                        <svg
                            class="h-6 w-6"
                            fill="currentColor"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            ><path
